hotel_text.important_information: Please inform Seaholic Apartment Central of your expected arrival time in advance. policies.content: You can cancel free of charge until 7 days before arrival. You'll be charged the total price of the reservation if you cancel in the 7 days before arrival. If you don’t show up you will be charged the total price of the reservation.

Up to two children from 4 to 18 year are charged  VND 100000 per night when using existing beds.
There is no capacity for extra beds in the room.
The maximum number of total guests in a room is 8.
There is no capacity for cribs in the room.
Additional fees are not calculated automatically in the total cost and will have to be paid for separately during your stay.
WiFi is available in all areas and is free of charge.
Private parking is available on site (reservation is not needed) and charges may apply.
Pets are not allowed.
You'll be charged a prepayment of the total price at any time.
